A User(A) will receive a Notification if a User(B) Shares a Post in this User's(A) Wall
A User will receive a Notification is he/she receives an Alert from a Moderator/Manager
A User will receive a Notification if he/she is Followed by another User				duplicated by first item
A User will receive a Notification if another User leave a comment after him under a post

A User will receive a Notification if a Moderator Deletes his/her Post				This should be Alert
A User will receive a Notification if a Moderator Deletes his/her Comment				This should be Alert

A User can see Notifications for new Followers
A User cna see Notifications for Likes to his/her Post
A User can see Notifications for Likes to his/her Comments
A User can see Notifications for new Comments
A User can see Notifications for being Mentioned in a Post
A User can see Notifications for being Mentioned in a Comment
A User can see Notifications for his/her Posts being Shared by another User
A User(A) can see Notifications if another User(B) Shares Posts on this User's(A) Wall
A User recieves a Notification if he/she is Followed

